  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/04fbb0acf72643363232a1be6e4a177a.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" width=256 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/04fbb0acf72643363232a1be6e4a177a.webm?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/04fbb0acf72643363232a1be6e4a177a.mp4?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/90cad57bc1f8c59c642f86b8474c342f.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" width=256 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/90cad57bc1f8c59c642f86b8474c342f.webm?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/90cad57bc1f8c59c642f86b8474c342f.mp4?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save the town festival in <strong>Marron's Day</strong>, a silly pocket-sized adventure where you're a bunny!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Marron, a young bunny, and help the cute animal friends in town so that they'll sign up for stalls at the town festival! Enjoy the cosy and retro pixel art graphics as you explore the town. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/0d7d263beb1fe2b6f02e7156016c8f16.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" width=256 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/0d7d263beb1fe2b6f02e7156016c8f16.webm?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/0d7d263beb1fe2b6f02e7156016c8f16.mp4?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/168eaf87263f2e3e4cb700ab5a52fa53.gif?t=1770038864\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/168eaf87263f2e3e4cb700ab5a52fa53.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A top-down town to explore and adorable animal friends to help </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosy minigames to go with a heartwarming story!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute pixel art and beepy chiptune music </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic retro gameplay - it can practically* run on the handheld game console of your childhood! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/3f975246c118511135107b2f166cb0cc.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" width=256 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/3f975246c118511135107b2f166cb0cc.webm?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/3f975246c118511135107b2f166cb0cc.mp4?t=1770038864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/d0f90953f7032983b8f5a7fd9a3d7d2a.gif?t=1770038864\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/d0f90953f7032983b8f5a7fd9a3d7d2a.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*(It really will run!)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use a controller, or for keyboard, use the following keys:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S key: Action / Use fishing rod)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D key: Cancel Reel in fish)</p></li></ul>",
