0953f7032983b8f5a7fd9a3d7d2a.gif?t=1770038864\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2620590/extras/d0f90953f7032983b8f5a7fd9a3d7d2a.poster.avif?t=1770038864\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*(It really will run!)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use a controller, or for keyboard, use the following keys:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S key: Action / Use fishing rod)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D key: Cancel Reel in fish)</p></li></ul>",
